visual.name: RadarChartByMAQSoftware
visual.description: Compare data across three or more variables in a single two-dimensional chart.

strokeWidth.description: Value must be less than or equal to 5

transparency.description: Set transparency for the plot color

circleRadius.description: Value must be less than or equal to 5

showDataPoints.description: Display data points on the plot

showValuesDataPoints.description: Display data values on the plot

showAllValuesDataPoints.description: Display all data values on the plot

dataPointColor.description: Change the color of the data points

plotValueColor.description: Change the color of the data values

fontFamily.description: Change the font family of labels

fontSize.description: Change the font size of legend
